FORM dan datalarni olish

formalarni olamiz va har birini postData degan funksiyani param iga beramiz
postData function: form ga submit dega hodisa ilazmiz preventDefault ni yozamiz, 
Dav: XML sorov yozamiz, POST server.php, const formData = new FormData(form), send(fornData), request load degan hodisa, 
formdatadan emas json: obj yasaymiz, formdatadagini objga yozamiz, obj json qilib olamiz, send(json), php ga qoshimcha kod

